Package: hellometry
Title: Biomass estimations for the BWG database and beyond
Version: 0.5.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pierre",
           family = "Rogy",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pierre.rogy@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3002-0059"))
Description: Estimates body size (mm) and biomass (mg) of bromeliad
    invertebrates from allometric relationships. Although developed for the
    Bromeliad Working Group (BWG) database, it works with any data that
    follow a few column-naming conventions.
